        <mxCell id="_hCXb_iJXr_RfH__JIMU-13" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontStyle=1;strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#99FFFF);" value="&lt;span data-start-index=&quot;775&quot; class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;Scrum nació en 1990, un contexto sin smartphones ni IA, diseñado para maximizar el trabajo entre humanos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-start-index=&quot;880&quot; class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="220" x="267" y="69" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="_hCXb_iJXr_RfH__JIMU-16" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontStyle=1;strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#99FFFF);" value="&lt;span data-start-index=&quot;894&quot; class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;El concepto de &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b data-start-index=&quot;910&quot; class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;Sprint&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span data-start-index=&quot;916&quot; class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt; (típicamente 2 semanas) pierde sentido cuando la IA permite incrementar el producto en horas o un par de días&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-start-index=&quot;1026&quot; class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="249" x="64" y="189" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="_hCXb_iJXr_RfH__JIMU-20" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontStyle=1;strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#99FFFF);" value="&lt;span data-start-index=&quot;1049&quot; class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;La alta productividad de la IA reduce el tamaño de los equipos; las ceremonias clásicas (dailies, retros) para equipos de 7-9 personas se vuelven ineficientes en micro-equipos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-start-index=&quot;1225&quot; class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="321" x="-5" y="344" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="_hCXb_iJXr_RfH__JIMU-23" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontStyle=1;strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#99FFFF);" value="&lt;span data-start-index=&quot;1238&quot; class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;Se pasa de un modelo 100% humano-humano a uno de &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b data-start-index=&quot;1288&quot; class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;humanos potenciados por IA y colaborando con IA&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-start-index=&quot;1335&quot; class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="226" x="168" y="483" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="_hCXb_iJXr_RfH__JIMU-26" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontStyle=1;strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#99FF99);" value="&lt;span data-start-index=&quot;1438&quot; class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;Evolución del Product Owner/Manager que ahora debe potenciar a sus equipos específicamente con IA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-start-index=&quot;1536&quot; class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
